{"tid":1136631,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特：波克夏買入了亞馬遜股票","createTime":"2019-05-03T06:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T19:00:54.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"6a3f5d64bf40c0a1da1c91558fd38774c3e68b3a","tid":1136631,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/05/03/phpvmcYS7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F05%2F03%2FphpvmcYS7.jpg&h=0afd34a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴菲特透露，波克夏公司已經買了亞馬遜股票。（資料照，法新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕「股神」巴菲特（Warren Buffett ）去年在波克夏（Berkshire Hathaway）股東大會上承認，當年沒有投資亞馬遜是個錯誤，但巴菲特近日接受媒體專訪，透露波克夏公司已經買入了亞馬遜股票。<br />\n<br />\n《CNBC》3日報導，巴菲特在今年的波克夏股東大會前夕接受專訪，他透露，波克夏辦公室裡管理資金的1名同事，已經買入了一些亞馬遜股票，這將在13F文件中顯示。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導認為，巴菲特指的同事，可能是Todd Combs或Ted Weschler，他們2人各自為波克夏管理價值逾130億美元的股票投資組合。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年的波克夏年度股東會將在4日登場，預計會有超過3萬名股東到內布拉斯加州奧瑪哈（Omaha）參與。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2778102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2778102&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=56d8c775\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2778102&h=45f3ef12\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2778102</a>"},{"pid":"fcacd08303f7baa96ccdd8cf673299b96c3c79f8","tid":1136631,"uid":26283,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"潮退時可以去amazon買底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c28b1841e43bccdaaefca5f12ebebbf62ab70e7","tid":1136631,"uid":1086,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:34:49.000Z","msg":"已經唔係佢既時代"},{"pid":"995331071a3b99e92f121011cda9be11948ed716","tid":11366